name: Feet Pose (realistic)
description:
LoRa model that allows you to generate some nice realistic feet (soles specifically).

Trained with Uber Realistic Porn Merge v1.3 (URPM), so I recommend using this model for better results.

I get good images with this setting :

  • 0.6 weigth for LoRa,

  • between 20-24 steps with Euler a,

  • simple prompt like "woman in bikini with beautiful feet, soles + Lora"

You can expect to generate one image with nearly perfect soles every 5 attempts or so, but feel free to explore others settings if you want.

Currently working on a new version for better accuracy and consistency. By the mean time, have fun and don't hesitate to share your images !
